name: Beyond Reality
description: There is a dimension, a dimension full of nonsense and surrealism. It is a place where crates are out to kill you, and a place where logic jumps off a bridge. A journey into a wondrous land of ludicrosity, your next stop: Beyond Reality! This WAD is playable on zdoom, skulltag, and zandronum, OpenGL is recommended to remove palette issues on some textures.
